1
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:09,400
Miss.

2
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,039
Xuelan.

3
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,530
Why are you here?

4
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,920
Young Master Bai.

5
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:23,770
This is news I heard recently at Baihua Tower.

6
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:36,360
Shen Zhao has close ties with so many people.

7
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:39,080
He intends to rebel.

8
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:42,520
The Emperor is unwell.

9
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,880
The court is in chaos.

10
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,050
Everyone is on edge.

11
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,759
Now that Marquis Bai is protecting the Third Prince,

12
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:48,960
the faster he moves,

13
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:51,490
the more likely he is to seize the initiative.

14
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,940
No wonder my father hasn't come back.

15
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,930
There is one more thing.

16
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,240
Shen Lingbo, the Second Miss of the Prime Minister's Manor,

17
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,880
is in close contact with Bulei.

18
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:03,600
You mean Shen Lingbo and Bulei?

19
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,920
Bulei has come to Baihua Tower many times.

20
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,280
He clears the place every time,

21
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,479
chasing everyone away,

22
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,960
to meet Shen Lingbo alone.

23
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:14,760
What exactly does Shen Lingbo want to do?

24
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:19,079
Perhaps she wants to use Bulei to get rid of Lord Shen.

25
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:21,840
Xuelan.

26
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,160
You told us all this.

27
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,860
Won't you be in danger?

28
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,410
I stopped caring about my life a long time ago.

29
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:32,440
If I can help Young Master Bai before I die,

30
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:33,960
that would be enough.

31
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,800
Don't be silly.

32
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,280
It's not that I'm not afraid of death.

33
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:40,340
I just think one should do something they won't regret.

34
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,079
Xuelan.

35
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,820
You helped me once.

36
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,060
I will definitely protect your life.

37
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,280
You can't protect me.

38
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:50,600
In this game, no one can protect anyone.

39
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,400
Miss Song.

40
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:55,640
I wish you two a long and happy life together.

41
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,040
Miss Shen.

42
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,400
I hate people who betray me the most.

43
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:10,120
I don't understand what you mean.

44
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:13,680
You really did harbor other thoughts about Manchuan.

45
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,600
I didn't.

46
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,880
If not, why did you go to the Marquis of Zhongyi's Manor?

47
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:20,280
Miss Shen, stop.

48
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:26,720
Those who betray me don't get a second chance.

49
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,600
Xuelan.

50
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:46,680
She was killed just like that.

51
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,920
If we don't escape,

52
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,320
we'll all end up like her.

53
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:57,480
Your Highness, why didn't you come with my father?

54
00:03:57,760 --> 00:04:00,690
Marquis Bai went to deal with the grassland cavalry.

55
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,660
Your Highness.

56
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:05,940
This is what Shen Lingbo asked Shen Qiangwei to give me.

57
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,960
What does it say?

58
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,360
The letter is very clear.

59
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,800
How Shen Zhao used the Emperor's illness as an excuse,

60
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,040
forged a decree to seize power,

61
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:17,519
and used my departure from the palace to set a trap to cut off reinforcements.

62
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:20,839
It also details Shen Lingbo's fake alliance with Bulei.

63
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,480
She even mentioned that?

64
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,000
She wrote clearly about how Bulei infiltrated Dasheng,

65
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,160
documenting every movement.

66
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,720
And the location where Bulei is hiding the grassland cavalry,

67
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,050
is also listed clearly.

68
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,840
This is practically a written indictment.

69
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:37,140
I don't understand why she would betray her own father.

70
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,760
The letter didn't say explicitly.

71
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:41,159
She only said she regards her father as an enemy,

72
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,690
not out of personal grudge.

73
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,720
Perhaps it's because Lord Shen treats human lives as worthless.

74
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,880
Or perhaps she just wants to survive.

75
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:50,240
To preserve her own life and status.

76
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:53,360
But she knew long ago that Shen Zhao was colluding with Bulei.

77
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,820
Yet she only speaks up now.

78
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:58,280
So she doesn't stand with Dasheng,

79
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,260
nor does she stand with us.

80
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,600
She is only on her own side.

81
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:05,280
So she betrayed her father.

82
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:07,610
Was it just to save herself?

83
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,280
Whatever the reason,

84
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,010
we must prepare in advance.

85
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,680
Why did you reveal where Bulei hid the grassland cavalry

86
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,440
to the Third Prince?

87
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,720
To lure Marquis Bai away.

88
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,880
Didn't you want to deal with Bulei?

89
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,000
How ruthless.

90
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,940
You got close to Song Xuan,

91
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,730
wanting to make a deal with her.

92
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,530
I won't stop you.

93
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:40,280
Aren't you afraid she'll actually agree?

94
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,680
I'm warning you too.

95
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,000
Don't try to play both sides.

96
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,080
It will backfire.

97
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,940
I've said this before.

98
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,960
You don't want to be my enemy.

99
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,880
If you choose Song Xuan,

100
00:05:57,159 --> 00:06:00,920
I guarantee your end will be ten thousand times worse than Bulei's.

101
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,080
Princess.

102
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,920
She dares speak to you like that?

103
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,850
I'll go kill her.

104
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,220
You can't kill her.

105
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,640
Then...

106
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,930
I intended for Song Xuan to deal with Shen Lingbo.

107
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:22,480
Now it seems we must change tactics.

108
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,290
The Emperor is critically ill.

109
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:26,240
He ordered me to preside over state affairs.

110
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,720
Marquis Bai Kui deceived the Third Prince.

111
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:31,600
The Emperor ordered me to bring the Third Prince back,

112
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:35,200
and take the Bai family back for trial.

113
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,260
Receive the edict.

114
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,720
The paper of the edict is old.

115
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,200
It is Dongcang paper.

116
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,530
This is no imperial decree.

117
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,480
It's a fake.

118
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,159
We will not accept it.

119
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,200
You dare defy the decree?

120
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:54,520
Lord Shen is flying into a rage out of shame.

121
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:56,480
Men, seize them!

122
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,540
Stand down.

123
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,200
Imperial Decree!

124
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,720
Shen Zhao plotted treason.

125
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,400
He attempted to usurp power with a fake decree.

126
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,730
His crimes are heinous.

127
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,880
I have served the Emperor for years.

128
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,480
What crime have I committed?

129
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,480
Shen Zhao, you...

130
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,000
You rats!

131
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,040
How could I lose to you?

132
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,520
Father, stop this.

133
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,720
Third Prince, my father committed treason.

134
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,450
I, Shen Lingbo, admit my guilt.

135
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,120
Rise.

136
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,200
The guilty official Shen Zhao is dead.

137
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:56,040
Shen Lingbo placed righteousness above family.

138
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,300
She deserves a reward.

139
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,000
You killed your father with your own hands.

140
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,200
For the greater good.

141
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,520
For the sake of the realm.

142
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,880
And for you.

143
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,200
Why did you kill your father?

144
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,640
I've lived by orders since I was a child.

145
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:14,400
Now I just want to act for myself for once.

146
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,650
You hate him.

147
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,080
It's not hate.

148
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,500
It's loathing.

149
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,720
Loathing that he saw me as a pawn.

150
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,720
Loathing that he treated me as a bargaining chip.

151
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:28,450
Loathing that he thought he could decide my life.

152
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:31,880
Manchuan.

153
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,320
Now nothing can stand in our way.

154
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,000
As long as you are by my side,

155
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,120
I fear nothing.

156
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:45,680
But he was your father.

157
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:46,920
You know,

158
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:49,960
he plotted to kill the entire Song Army.

159
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,760
He also killed my mother.

160
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,100
He deserved to die.

161
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:57,200
The law would have punished his crimes.

162
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:00,360
Don't you hate him at all?

163
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,330
He almost killed Song Xuan.

164
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,490
I killed him for you.

165
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,640
And you actually blame me?

166
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,520
I do hate him.

167
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,800
But that doesn't justify using your hands to kill him.

168
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,520
How can you say that about me?

169
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:17,370
I thought you were the only one who understood me.

170
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:21,840
Manchuan, I did all this for you.

171
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,690
I'm leaving.

172
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,120
Madam Hua.

173
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,240
Coming, Young Master Bai.

174
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:30,120
Why haven't I seen Xuelan lately?

175
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:32,800
She went back to her hometown.

176
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,640
Without leaving a word?

177
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,400
She said she didn't want to worry you,

178
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,760
so she told us not to say much.

179
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,320
I see.

180
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,400
What did that look you just gave me mean?

181
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,240
Did you want Manchuan to suspect me?

182
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,080
I... I didn't.

183
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,170
I wouldn't dare.

184
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,920
I didn't...

185
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,000
You're lying.

186
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,880
I... well...

187
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,200
While I was away,

188
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,240
did someone say something to Manchuan?

189
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,570
Spare... spare my life!

190
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:05,560
Anyway, if anyone did say anything,

191
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,560
I'll send you to join Xiang Xuelan in the grave.
